  "body": "This still needs some tests but I wanted to get this open for feedback in the meantime.\n\nThe modifications allow macro expansions in type positions:\n\n``` rust\ntrait HList {}\n\nstruct HNil;\nstruct HCons<H, T: HList>(H, T);\n\nimpl HList for HNil {}\nimpl<H, T: HList> HList for HCons<H, T> {}\n\nmacro_rules! HList {\n    () => (HNil);\n    ($head:ty) => (HCons<$head, HNil>);\n    ($head:ty, $($tail:ty),*) => (HCons<$head, HList!($($tail),*)>);\n}\n\nfn foo(_xs: HList![ bool, u64, u16, (), &'static str ]) -> HList![ String ] {\n    unimplemented!()\n}\n\nfn main() {\n    let _ = Vec::<HList![ bool, u64, u16 ]>::new();\n}\n```\n",
